#: download.html%2Bsection.div.div.h3:46-7
msgid "Important:"
msgstr ""

#: download.html%2Bsection.div.div.p:47-7
msgid ""
"Ceno has two modes of operation - <strong>Public</strong> and "
"<strong>Personal</strong>. You can easily toggle between them. Public mode "
"offers the best connectivity but the least privacy - websites that you visit "
"or share are recorded in a publicly-accessible registry (BitTorrent). "
"Personal mode eliminates this record but may be slower and less efficient at "
"retrieving content. See the <a href=\"support.html\">FAQ</a> or <a href=\"../"
"user-manual/\">User Manual</a> for more details on Ceno usage."
msgstr ""

